e village totally adores Princes Claire, and it wants to take her away~. I won't let that happen!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event116-03-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"Lisa... Aren't you getting a little too into this...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event116-03-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"Now that the story has progressed, we should return to the castle for now. ヾ(*´ω`)ﾉﾞ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event116-03-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Demon Princess Ako","body":"We're back, your majesty~! We asked about those rumors from before~! Okay, let's try talking to him again...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event116-03-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"King of Yorbei","body":"Oh, young ones. So you have information on what we previously discussed! Well done!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"Nice work. (´∀`∩ With this, the first stage of the quest is complete. (*'-'*)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event116-03-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"King of Yorbei","body":"Yes, I see... What?! A dragon is after my daughter Claire?! This calls for action!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"King of Yorbei","body":"The creature likely dwells within the mountains to the north. Unfortunately, the journey alone would take a month... Perhaps there is a way to lure the beast out of hiding...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"King of Yorbei","body":"... Aha! I can have one of you skilled adventurers pose as my daughter during the wedding and then exterminate the monster...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"This king... He's deciding everything while we have no say in the matter.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event116-03-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"That is how games are.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event116-03-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"King of Yorbei","body":"On the morning of the wedding, the bride is to be crowned at the cathedral with the Tiara of Blessing, an item passed down by the royal family.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"King of Yorbei","body":"I will have you wait and hide at that cathedral, then face the dragon once it arrives. Do not fail!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Do not fail...? What exactly does he want us to do?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event116-03-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"The first part was gathering info, but it looks like this is going to be a battle quest. o(>ω<)o","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf_right01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event116-03-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Demon Princess Ako","body":"Now we're getting somewhere~! I'm itching for some action~! Ah, look! Someone else is coming!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event116-03-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Guard","body":"Your majesty! I bring dire news! Thieves have stolen the Tiara of Blessing!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Whaaat?! What's with this sudden twist?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event116-03-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"King of Yorbei","body":"The wedding cannot take place without the Tiara of Blessing... Adventurers, could you first help us retrieve this most important treasure?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"H-hold on... They let a bunch of thieves steal such an important item... Is this king's head on straight...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event116-03-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"That is how games are.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event116-03-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Whoa, something popped up! Is this a new quest?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event116-03-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Demon Princess Ako","body":"Hmmm, let's see here. It says, \"Retrieve the Tiara of Blessing from the Thieves\"!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event116-03-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Demon Princess Ako","body":"Sounds like a plan to me! Just click the accept button, and...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event116-03-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"King of Yorbei","body":"Excellent! You have my thanks, adventurers! The thieves who stole the Tiara of Blessing have made their hideout in the Yorbei Mines to the east!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Demon Princess Ako","body":"Okay~! You can count on us! Alright, everyone, let's get to work!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event116-03-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Hmmm, so we need to head to the eastern mines first, take back the Tiara of Blessing, and then destroy the dragon... Is that right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event116-03-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Yes, from what I can tell. However, I believe we will also need to do some grinding.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event116-03-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"Grinding?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event116-03-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"It means raising our characters' levels. o(>ω<)o","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event116-03-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"Imai-san and Yukina-san, your HP is so low that even a couple of hits from some low level mobs would put you out of commission. (TдT; )","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event116-03-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Demon Princess Ako","body":"And the best way to increase your HP is to level up.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event116-03-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"I see... But doing that sounds like it would take a long time...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event116-03-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"No, that is not the case at all. Accepting quests appropriate for your level is the quickest way to level up in the world of NFO.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event116-03-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"Hikawa-san is right. ヾ(*´ω`)ﾉ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event116-03-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"This event was originally planned for immediately after the game's launch, so the level requirements shouldn't be all that high. (q'∀'o)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event116-03-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"A little grinding here and there while we play the mission should be enough to clear the quest.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event116-03-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Demon Princess Ako","body":"Uh-huh! And the rest of us will give you plenty of buffs to help keep your stats up, so don't worry!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event116-03-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Ohhh, so that's what buff means...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event116-03-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"Buffs are unique abilities that enhance your stats. Debuffs are abilities that lower the stats of others.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event116-03-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"I get it now~. Well, we've got a bunch of tough allies on our side, so why don't we give it a shot, Yukina?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event116-03-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"If that is the plan, then I will simply follow suit.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf_right01","expressi